line_1: "Grete clerk of Fame' is house, whose excellence
line_2: "Maie wele befitt thilk place of eminence,

line_1: If not thy bliss, thy excellence,
Beauty is but your second Excellence.
line_2: So shall the wond'ring World be taught from thence,
Embraces Virtue from a nobler sense
